WEBVTT

00:06.499 --> 00:07.840
(Respect copyright)

00:14.112 --> 00:20.704
♪Memories hold you back
from fulfilling your dreams♪

00:24.288 --> 00:30.432
♪Only by moving forward
can you find reunion♪

00:32.640 --> 00:35.872
♪Endings only mark new routes♪

00:36.096 --> 00:42.112
♪It's all part of the scenery♪

00:42.432 --> 00:45.856
♪To the horizon's call♪

00:45.920 --> 00:52.480
♪Your journey hasn't started♪

00:53.536 --> 00:57.472
♪Towards mountains,
chase the stars bright♪

00:57.472 --> 01:03.552
♪Let time embrace you
and wash away the past♪

01:03.840 --> 01:07.712
♪Put every twist behind you♪

01:07.712 --> 01:12.576
♪Drift leisurely through time♪

01:12.960 --> 01:15.680
♪Make headway against the wind♪

01:15.680 --> 01:18.667
♪Let mountains bow to your pace♪

01:18.720 --> 01:24.128
♪Rush towards a life without regret♪

01:24.640 --> 01:28.579
♪Let your nature burst free♪

01:30.240 --> 01:34.490
=The First Jasmine=

01:34.960 --> 01:37.644
=Episode 14=

01:38.291 --> 01:39.170
Why did you run?

01:39.411 --> 01:41.730
Come on. Let's go home.

01:43.771 --> 01:44.571
Wait.

01:46.810 --> 01:47.610
Take it.

01:47.730 --> 01:50.411
Li, what did you see?

01:51.530 --> 01:55.011
The Wang family of the south offers
a golden-thread nanmu longevity cane.

01:55.250 --> 01:57.411
Wishing Madam a long, long life.

01:58.890 --> 02:03.330
Zuixian Tower offers 16 boxes of peach
cakes with the 100-blessings pattern.

02:03.970 --> 02:05.651
Wishing Madam endless happiness.

02:07.330 --> 02:08.011
Slow down.

02:08.011 --> 02:08.851
Rong.

02:08.851 --> 02:09.811
Wishing Madam longevity.

02:12.330 --> 02:14.210
Wishing Madam happiness and good health.

02:15.091 --> 02:16.851
- How is it?
- Register them all.

02:16.851 --> 02:17.450
Alright.

02:17.531 --> 02:18.210
Slow down.

02:18.971 --> 02:21.371
Make sure you match the heights
and colors properly.

02:21.490 --> 02:22.210
(Ye Mansion)
You are here.

02:22.210 --> 02:24.531
Welcome! Please come inside.

02:26.371 --> 02:26.871
Alright.

02:30.170 --> 02:31.170
Master Wenshen.

02:31.170 --> 02:32.080
Mr. Fu.

02:32.080 --> 02:34.210
Madam will be delighted to see you.

02:34.371 --> 02:34.890
Good.

02:35.170 --> 02:35.670
Please.

02:35.971 --> 02:37.330
Did anyone come for me today?

02:38.011 --> 02:38.650
No.

02:39.371 --> 02:40.691
Good, that's good.

02:44.610 --> 02:46.730
Your Highness. Please come in.

02:47.251 --> 02:47.890
Master Wenshen.

02:47.890 --> 02:50.091
Prince Ding has arrived!

02:52.091 --> 02:53.450
- Greetings, Your Highness.
- Greetings, Your Highness.

02:54.490 --> 02:55.930
- Greetings, Your Highness.
- Greetings, Your Highness.

02:57.571 --> 02:59.851
Madam, you are truly blessed.

03:00.330 --> 03:03.730
Look, all your grandchildren
have come to see you.

03:03.730 --> 03:04.371
Exactly.

03:06.170 --> 03:08.770
Mom, can I have all these candies?

03:09.571 --> 03:11.170
How many candies have you eaten today?

03:11.371 --> 03:12.490
I won't tell you.

03:14.610 --> 03:16.330
- Greetings, Your Highness.
- Greetings, Your Highness.

03:16.571 --> 03:18.411
Ye Li, these are all for you.

03:19.050 --> 03:19.851
Thank you.

03:21.210 --> 03:22.210
Li, you're here.

03:22.210 --> 03:23.571
Let me introduce you.

03:23.571 --> 03:25.691
They're your Fourth Great-Uncle
and Sixth Great-Uncle.

03:25.691 --> 03:27.210
They just returned from Lanyi.

03:27.210 --> 03:29.011
And this is your Fourth Aunt.

03:29.011 --> 03:30.971
She used to hold you
when you were little.

03:32.210 --> 03:34.811
Greetings, Fourth Great-Uncle,
Sixth Great-Uncle, and Fourth Aunt.

03:35.050 --> 03:39.170
Mom, I came across
this auspicious item during my travels.

03:39.251 --> 03:41.890
Today, I present it to you specially.

03:42.330 --> 03:44.571
May you live long and well.

03:45.851 --> 03:47.571
Little Li has grown so much.

03:48.490 --> 03:51.571
Not 'Little Li' anymore.
Now we must call her Princess Ding.

03:52.811 --> 03:53.971
She'll keep them for me.

03:55.531 --> 03:56.730
Let me place it for you.

03:57.811 --> 03:59.890
A touch of luck
for your birthday peaches.

04:00.691 --> 04:01.490
Look at it.

04:04.531 --> 04:06.610
Grandmother, Ye Li wishes you
a happy birthday.

04:06.610 --> 04:09.811
Wishing you everlasting happiness,
longevity, and good health.

04:10.490 --> 04:11.291
Wanzhou,

04:12.210 --> 04:13.291
you're here.

04:13.971 --> 04:14.971
Stand up.

04:16.171 --> 04:17.171
You've lost weight.

04:18.330 --> 04:19.330
Tired, aren't you?

04:20.410 --> 04:23.931
Li, didn't His Highness come with you?

04:25.171 --> 04:27.491
His Highness is busy with duties
and couldn't get away.

04:27.611 --> 04:32.970
Prince Ding just became Jingzhao Prefect
and is, of course, overwhelmed by work.

04:33.251 --> 04:36.330
Prince Li didn't come in person either.

04:36.770 --> 04:37.890
Yes, indeed.

04:40.210 --> 04:41.210
That's true.

04:45.530 --> 04:47.731
Ms. Wang, where is Wenhua?

04:48.410 --> 04:49.210
Where is he?

04:50.571 --> 04:52.491
Mr. Fu, go and get him quickly.

04:54.611 --> 04:56.530
901, 902,

04:56.530 --> 04:58.970
903, 904,

04:58.970 --> 05:01.051
905, 906,

05:01.051 --> 05:02.090
907...

05:02.290 --> 05:03.090
Master Wenhua.

05:07.290 --> 05:08.090
Master Wenhua,

05:10.290 --> 05:11.731
all the guests have arrived.

05:11.731 --> 05:13.371
Madam is asking you.

05:13.890 --> 05:17.890
The servants said you haven't had
a full night's sleep for days.

05:18.131 --> 05:20.970
Besides, today is Madam's birthday.

05:21.131 --> 05:22.448
All the clan elders are here.

05:23.536 --> 05:25.770
You should at least show your face.

05:29.970 --> 05:33.011
Moreover, both princess consorts
have returned.

05:33.330 --> 05:35.970
Just go to the banquet,
have a few bites, and come back.

05:35.970 --> 05:37.330
It won't take you long.

05:44.330 --> 05:45.571
How many are left?

05:46.571 --> 05:48.731
Eighty-two more are needed.

05:49.410 --> 05:51.290
Almost there. You can continue
once you're back.

05:51.890 --> 05:52.970
Please, Master Wenhua.

05:59.371 --> 06:01.371
Master Wenhua, are you alright?

06:02.691 --> 06:05.731
Keep an eye on everything.
The Daoist master will arrive tomorrow.

06:06.090 --> 06:06.890
- Yes.
- Yes.

06:13.611 --> 06:18.011
Madam Ye is truly blessed.
She has such a big family.

06:18.011 --> 06:19.051
Come and catch me!

06:19.051 --> 06:20.450
Thank you, everyone.

06:20.530 --> 06:24.330
Thank you all for attending
my mother's birthday banquet.

06:27.890 --> 06:28.890
The dance is really good.

06:28.890 --> 06:30.450
Let me toast everyone.

06:30.450 --> 06:31.011
Look.

06:31.931 --> 06:32.491
Come on.

06:32.811 --> 06:35.290
- Come on.
- Okay.

06:35.410 --> 06:36.330
Drink!

06:36.330 --> 06:37.171
Come on.

06:47.650 --> 06:49.290
- Good.
- Good.

06:49.931 --> 06:52.330
Mom, they have come to toast.

06:52.330 --> 06:53.131
Madam.

06:53.330 --> 06:55.970
- Wishing you eternal life!
- Wishing you eternal life!

07:05.611 --> 07:07.251
Greetings, Your Highness.

07:07.811 --> 07:12.330
I heard Prince Ding is Jingzhao Prefect
now and is highly valued by His Majesty.

07:12.410 --> 07:15.491
Truly a talented young man
with a bright future.

07:18.931 --> 07:22.770
Good. Please take your seats.
Thank you all.

07:24.144 --> 07:29.264
(Auspicious Omens)

07:31.290 --> 07:32.251
Who is that?

07:32.251 --> 07:33.290
It's Prince Li.

07:34.691 --> 07:35.731
It's Prince Li?

07:36.011 --> 07:38.210
- Right.
- Why has Prince Li come?

07:38.571 --> 07:40.491
It must be for Princess Li.

07:41.611 --> 07:45.330
The Ye family is truly prosperous.
With filial children and grandchildren,

07:45.530 --> 07:47.171
it has also produced two princesses.

07:59.811 --> 08:00.731
Are you full?

08:02.011 --> 08:02.970
Have some more.

08:11.691 --> 08:12.770
What else would you like?

08:13.611 --> 08:14.571
Just those strips.

08:37.971 --> 08:39.131
Bravo!

08:48.570 --> 08:52.011
Prince Li's guqin playing
is extraordinary, truly heavenly music.

08:52.011 --> 08:55.091
Madam is truly blessed. Prince Li
himself came to honor her birthday.

08:55.091 --> 08:55.611
Indeed.

08:56.810 --> 08:58.690
I wish to use this piece,
Green Plum Prelude,

08:58.731 --> 09:01.930
to wish Madam long-lasting
blessings and longevity.

09:03.770 --> 09:06.170
You are so thoughtful.

09:07.731 --> 09:09.930
I didn't know
you were coming, Prince Li.

09:09.930 --> 09:11.011
Forgive my lack of welcome.

09:12.530 --> 09:13.530
Please take a seat.

09:18.131 --> 09:19.331
Go back to your mom.

09:21.731 --> 09:23.290
Everyone, please take your seats.

09:23.290 --> 09:25.091
Alright, continue.

09:36.131 --> 09:37.451
I'll announce you.

09:37.451 --> 09:39.451
Move aside.

09:40.530 --> 09:41.091
Well...

09:41.410 --> 09:43.451
It's Madam Ye's birthday.
Forgive me for being late.

09:43.930 --> 09:47.410
But today I must ask Master Wenshen out
for a word about an urgent matter.

09:49.930 --> 09:52.290
Ye Wenshen! Ye Wenshen, stop there!

09:55.770 --> 09:58.290
General Wang, y-you are here.

09:58.530 --> 10:01.611
Ye Wenshen, be wise
and come out with me.

10:01.810 --> 10:05.371
Today is your mother's birthday feast,
and I've already shown you enough face.

10:06.491 --> 10:08.491
Sir, I greet you.

10:08.491 --> 10:11.251
This is my third brother.
And today is my mom's birthday.

10:11.930 --> 10:13.530
If there is something, tell me.

10:13.810 --> 10:15.331
Good news can be discussed nicely.

10:16.570 --> 10:20.331
But this scoundrel seduced my wife
and brought turmoil to my household.

10:20.331 --> 10:21.290
He's utterly shameless!

10:22.170 --> 10:24.290
Tell me, how can I discuss it nicely?

10:24.371 --> 10:26.611
Stop! Let go of your hand!

10:28.371 --> 10:29.971
If I did it, I'd pay for it.

10:33.211 --> 10:34.570
But I didn't do it!

10:34.810 --> 10:36.530
Beat me to death,
and I still didn't do it.

10:40.851 --> 10:41.650
What do you want?

10:42.530 --> 10:43.530
Dare to do, not admit?

10:43.530 --> 10:45.770
- Wait, under the emperor's nose...
- What...

10:45.770 --> 10:46.770
Dare to do, not admit?

10:46.770 --> 10:47.570
In broad daylight...

10:47.810 --> 10:48.410
General Wang.

10:48.410 --> 10:49.170
Move aside!

10:50.410 --> 10:51.211
Stop him!

10:52.971 --> 10:53.770
Let me go!

10:54.131 --> 10:54.930
Take him away.

10:55.131 --> 10:55.690
Go!

10:56.091 --> 10:56.890
Go!

11:03.851 --> 11:04.650
Your Highness.

11:07.570 --> 11:08.971
Wishing Madam a happy birthday.

11:10.930 --> 11:11.731
Ling'er.

11:14.131 --> 11:16.011
Your Highness, drink a little less.

11:17.251 --> 11:18.050
It's fine.

11:19.971 --> 11:22.331
Prince Ding is swamped
by official matters

11:22.331 --> 11:23.371
and can't come in person.

11:23.530 --> 11:25.971
He specially sent me
to present a birthday gift.

11:29.770 --> 11:33.091
Made from Zhongnan Mountain's cold jade,
the pillow is soaked in nurturing herbs,

11:33.170 --> 11:35.930
according to Sun Simiao's
Prescriptions Worth a Thousand Gold.

11:35.971 --> 11:38.810
With this gift,
we wish Madam good health.

11:39.410 --> 11:41.410
Good, good.

11:47.731 --> 11:48.530
Master Ye.

11:50.331 --> 11:52.211
Please come with me
to the prefectural office.

11:52.731 --> 11:54.211
I-I have to go too?

11:55.770 --> 11:58.570
Mom, it's fine.
I'll go and come right back.

11:58.890 --> 12:00.371
Wending, tell Mom.

12:00.371 --> 12:01.211
Alright.

12:02.371 --> 12:03.170
Okay.

12:06.331 --> 12:08.530
Mom, Wenshen will come back shortly.

12:08.611 --> 12:10.170
It's alright.

12:14.971 --> 12:17.331
Your Highness, you seem tired.

12:18.570 --> 12:23.611
Someone, help His Highness to rest
and take good care of him.

12:24.170 --> 12:26.290
Your Highness, come on.

12:27.170 --> 12:28.170
You don't need to go.

12:28.770 --> 12:30.770
Stay with your mother
and keep an eye here.

12:30.770 --> 12:31.451
Be careful.

12:54.971 --> 12:55.930
It's fine.

12:58.170 --> 12:59.770
Please go back. Stop here.

13:00.091 --> 13:00.971
Alright.

13:02.530 --> 13:03.290
Take care.

13:03.290 --> 13:06.731
Uncle, it's getting late.
I should go back.

13:06.731 --> 13:07.331
Alright then.

13:07.331 --> 13:08.530
Li, are you leaving?

13:08.851 --> 13:10.770
Yes, I'm leaving.

13:10.810 --> 13:14.091
Don't go. It'll be dark
by the time you get back.

13:14.570 --> 13:17.211
You and Ying rarely visit.
Neither of you should leave.

13:17.211 --> 13:19.971
I've already talked to Ying.
She's staying.

13:21.770 --> 13:24.331
Li, please stay.

13:24.890 --> 13:27.731
Yes, Li. Just stay for one night.

13:27.971 --> 13:30.890
You left home as a child
and are not very close to us.

13:31.690 --> 13:34.971
But you must know,
no matter where you marry,

13:35.331 --> 13:37.290
you're still a daughter
of the Ye family.

13:38.971 --> 13:43.331
From now on in the capital, remember
that blood ties are the most important.

13:43.770 --> 13:44.930
You're right, Uncle.

13:45.290 --> 13:46.410
Then I'll go with you.

13:54.770 --> 13:55.890
Why aren't you scared?

13:56.491 --> 13:57.410
Why should I be?

13:59.011 --> 13:59.890
Where did you get it?

14:00.410 --> 14:02.131
I caught it at the banquet just now.

14:02.690 --> 14:04.331
You could catch this at the banquet?

14:04.890 --> 14:06.731
It tried to scurry past under the table.

14:06.770 --> 14:08.690
I reached out and blocked it.

14:09.890 --> 14:11.211
It's a stupid toad.

14:11.851 --> 14:13.971
Why did you grab it? It's dirty.

14:13.971 --> 14:14.971
Just leave it here.

14:16.410 --> 14:17.211
No.

14:17.211 --> 14:20.170
I'm going to scare Ye Ying with it.
She'll definitely be afraid.

14:22.170 --> 14:23.731
Does that cripple treat you well?

14:25.930 --> 14:27.170
If you call him that again,

14:27.170 --> 14:28.971
I'll stuff this toad into your mouth.

14:29.011 --> 14:30.170
I'm your brother.

14:30.170 --> 14:33.371
A half-brother by my stepmother?
No different from a toad.

14:33.971 --> 14:35.890
I'm much more useful than it.

14:36.890 --> 14:39.770
Wait, why am I comparing
myself to a toad?

14:42.331 --> 14:43.890
You'll need me someday.

14:46.971 --> 14:48.530
Qingyu, chase it with me!

14:48.810 --> 14:49.611
Your Highness.

14:50.690 --> 14:51.570
Slow down.

14:53.650 --> 14:55.251
(Mom! Mom!)

15:08.976 --> 15:13.173
♪Time has kept some lines alive♪

15:15.131 --> 15:20.050
(Mom, when will the tree
we planted grow up?)

15:22.170 --> 15:23.211
When you grow up,

15:25.371 --> 15:27.170
it will shelter you from wind and rain.

15:28.491 --> 15:29.491
Little muddy kitten.

15:30.091 --> 15:30.890
Mom!

15:31.570 --> 15:32.650
Little muddy kitten!

15:32.810 --> 15:34.371
Mom, stop it!

15:34.371 --> 15:35.011
(Little kitten!)

15:35.011 --> 15:36.770
(Mom, catch me! Come on!)

15:38.096 --> 15:41.424
♪After clouds that winds pursue♪

15:41.424 --> 15:44.874
♪You can silently watch each sunrise♪

15:44.874 --> 15:48.422
♪Finding happiness by your side♪

15:48.422 --> 15:51.910
♪You don't need to chart a map♪

15:51.910 --> 15:55.222
♪Of every bend where love winds on♪

15:55.222 --> 15:58.553
♪Nor travel far to guide its course♪

15:58.553 --> 16:04.145
♪To warm your heart♪

16:35.770 --> 16:39.170
Li, you must protect this well.
Come with me.

16:41.810 --> 16:42.890
Hide inside. Be quiet.

16:44.491 --> 16:45.251
Search it!

16:47.011 --> 16:47.770
Open the door!

16:48.410 --> 16:49.251
- Open the door!
- Open it!

16:50.890 --> 16:51.530
Yanlu.

16:52.611 --> 16:53.371
Stay back!

16:54.690 --> 16:55.770
Hand it over!

16:57.851 --> 16:58.650
Wenhua.

17:01.371 --> 17:04.891
Wanzhou, listen to Wending.
Hand over the imperial edict.

17:05.251 --> 17:06.370
That thing is a curse.

17:08.011 --> 17:08.610
Search!

17:08.770 --> 17:09.691
Who dares!

17:11.451 --> 17:15.211
By doing this, you're making everyone
in the mansion die with you. Is that it?

17:17.691 --> 17:21.011
Wenhua, we can't do that.

17:21.651 --> 17:23.610
We'll get General Mo killed.

17:24.050 --> 17:27.050
My father has come down the mountain.
Please, go find him.

17:27.810 --> 17:30.451
Listen to Wending and hand it over.

17:31.370 --> 17:32.171
Hold her down!

17:32.171 --> 17:32.691
Go!

17:33.691 --> 17:35.050
My lady! My lady!

17:35.411 --> 17:36.290
- Let me go!
- Search!

17:36.290 --> 17:36.931
Search!

17:36.931 --> 17:38.211
- Let me go!
- Wenhua!

17:38.211 --> 17:39.530
No! Let me go!

17:39.530 --> 17:40.491
Search!

17:40.810 --> 17:41.530
No!

17:44.251 --> 17:45.251
Let me go!

17:48.810 --> 17:49.971
Wenhua!

17:53.011 --> 17:53.731
No!

17:55.370 --> 17:56.370
Give me the edict!

17:57.090 --> 17:58.011
- Give me the edict!
- Let go!

17:58.011 --> 17:58.731
Li!

17:59.530 --> 18:00.130
Give it to me!

18:00.691 --> 18:01.330
Li!

18:01.330 --> 18:02.011
Mom!

18:02.011 --> 18:02.731
Let go!

18:04.251 --> 18:04.891
Give it to me!

18:04.891 --> 18:05.411
Mom!

18:05.411 --> 18:05.931
Give it!

18:05.931 --> 18:07.691
Mom! Mom!

18:07.691 --> 18:09.891
My lady! Let go of me!

18:09.891 --> 18:11.050
You wretch, get lost!

18:13.090 --> 18:14.090
- You wretch!
- Give it to me!

18:14.090 --> 18:14.610
Let go!

18:14.691 --> 18:15.370
Yanlu?

18:15.370 --> 18:16.530
Yanlu!

18:16.530 --> 18:17.211
Give it to me!

18:20.731 --> 18:22.971
Li? Li? Are you all right?

18:26.160 --> 18:29.040
(Edict)

18:33.570 --> 18:34.491
- Ye Wending!
- Go!

18:34.491 --> 18:35.731
Give me back the edict!

18:36.971 --> 18:40.171
Wenhua! Wenhua, I beg you, help me!

18:40.171 --> 18:42.931
My father will be here soon.
We promised General Mo...

18:42.931 --> 18:44.651
Wanzhou, don't be like this.

18:44.651 --> 18:47.011
Calm down. Calm down.

18:48.491 --> 18:49.171
I'm sorry.

18:50.090 --> 18:52.691
Wenhua, who sent you?

18:52.691 --> 18:53.570
(Who sent you?)

18:53.570 --> 18:55.251
(Mom! Mom!)

18:56.130 --> 18:56.850
Mom!

18:57.971 --> 18:59.090
(Open the door, Mom!)

19:01.171 --> 19:02.731
Mom? Mom?

19:03.971 --> 19:05.931
Mom? Mom?

19:06.211 --> 19:08.130
Mom, how are you? Mom?

19:08.971 --> 19:11.570
Mom! Mom!

19:13.931 --> 19:14.731
Mom.

19:16.971 --> 19:19.570
Mom, are you sick?

19:19.810 --> 19:22.691
I will get a physician.
Mom, don't scare me.

19:24.290 --> 19:25.090
Li.

19:30.130 --> 19:30.850
Mom.

19:32.451 --> 19:33.251
Li.

19:35.451 --> 19:36.570
I'm

19:37.850 --> 19:39.011
done for.

19:41.050 --> 19:44.530
Go somewhere for me.

19:45.290 --> 19:47.011
All right, Mom.

19:48.451 --> 19:49.411
Where?

19:50.530 --> 19:52.211
To the execution ground.

19:54.411 --> 19:55.931
Find Mo Xiuwen

19:57.011 --> 20:00.610
and tell him I'm done for.

20:02.211 --> 20:04.370
I have failed him.

20:05.211 --> 20:08.011
Ask him if there's anything
we can do for him.

20:08.810 --> 20:12.050
All right, Mom.
I'll go to the execution ground,

20:12.850 --> 20:13.971
find Mo Xiuwen,

20:14.491 --> 20:19.451
tell him, and ask him if there's
anything else we can do for him.

20:22.011 --> 20:22.731
Mom.

20:25.491 --> 20:26.251
Li.

20:26.251 --> 20:26.971
Mom.

20:29.211 --> 20:30.011
(Mom!)

20:34.320 --> 20:37.616
(Blessed by Heaven)

20:40.770 --> 20:41.530
Mom.

21:13.130 --> 21:15.731
Li, why are you here?

21:18.451 --> 21:19.770
Am I dreaming?

21:26.130 --> 21:27.290
So it's a dream.

21:35.570 --> 21:36.370
Li.

21:38.090 --> 21:40.891
Why are you so angry, even in my dream?

21:43.011 --> 21:45.090
Don't move. Behave.

21:55.211 --> 21:56.171
It hurts.

22:05.530 --> 22:06.971
At Lishan Academy,

22:08.290 --> 22:09.691
what on earth did you go through?

22:09.850 --> 22:12.491
Why do you have
so many scars on your arm?

22:13.050 --> 22:13.971
Monkeys bit me.

22:15.251 --> 22:17.651
Since when did Lishan Academy
have monkeys?

22:19.770 --> 22:20.451
It hurts.

22:21.850 --> 22:23.050
Isn't this a dream?

22:24.530 --> 22:25.931
Can you feel pain in a dream?

22:26.050 --> 22:26.850
Li,

22:29.810 --> 22:30.891
I missed you so much.

22:33.251 --> 22:34.810
So much.

22:37.850 --> 22:39.850
I really missed you.

22:40.050 --> 22:43.491
Li, I really missed...

23:00.931 --> 23:02.090
Li,

23:04.050 --> 23:04.850
do you know?

23:06.491 --> 23:07.290
Today,

23:09.370 --> 23:11.211
I'm going to the Ye Mansion to see you.

23:13.330 --> 23:15.011
I'm going to play

23:16.211 --> 23:18.011
Green Plum Prelude for you.

23:19.290 --> 23:20.370
Do you remember?

23:21.610 --> 23:24.370
Master Yu taught us that tune.

23:25.971 --> 23:28.130
Back then, you could play it
after hearing it once.

23:29.530 --> 23:30.330
Li,

23:31.211 --> 23:34.050
I practiced the Green Plum Prelude
for a long time.

23:35.370 --> 23:36.211
I don't know

23:38.530 --> 23:39.971
if you'll like it.

23:42.330 --> 23:44.370
I've also prepared some mulberry wine.

23:44.610 --> 23:49.130
Back at Lishan Mountain,
a hunter gave two jars to Master Zhu.

23:50.050 --> 23:52.971
You secretly drank half a jar back then.

23:53.570 --> 23:56.850
Then you passed out on my guqin table.

24:00.211 --> 24:02.370
Li, do you

24:04.451 --> 24:05.931
still love drinking now?

24:20.491 --> 24:21.290
Li,

24:22.931 --> 24:25.570
do you really hate me?

24:29.931 --> 24:34.090
Actually, I hate myself too.

24:34.651 --> 24:38.530
You never let me explain
about that matter.

24:39.891 --> 24:42.570
Actually, I don't know
how to explain it either.

24:45.011 --> 24:48.731
Sometimes I feel innocent,

24:49.810 --> 24:51.290
forced, and helpless.

24:53.491 --> 24:56.211
Sometimes I feel I deserve to die.

24:57.691 --> 24:59.770
If I had died with them,

25:00.330 --> 25:03.850
would you have been
a little kinder to me?

25:05.770 --> 25:06.651
But now,

25:08.891 --> 25:12.290
I have so many things left undone.

25:14.290 --> 25:15.251
I want to die.

25:17.011 --> 25:17.770
But

25:20.850 --> 25:22.090
do I have the right?

25:26.370 --> 25:29.570
I guess you don't like hearing this.

25:30.651 --> 25:34.850
But when I see you,
I always want to say something.

25:35.651 --> 25:37.211
Now that you're in my dream,

25:40.651 --> 25:41.891
just indulge me.

25:47.130 --> 25:48.411
I'll have someone clean it up.

25:49.570 --> 25:50.411
Are you leaving?

25:54.610 --> 25:55.411
Forget it.

25:57.451 --> 25:58.330
You can go.

26:00.610 --> 26:01.651
To have this dream,

26:02.850 --> 26:04.211
I'm already very content.

26:05.370 --> 26:08.770
I really wish this dream
would never end.

26:25.072 --> 26:28.944
(Jingzhao Prefecture)

26:39.610 --> 26:42.370
Your Highness, the gift has been
delivered to the Ye Mansion.

26:42.770 --> 26:45.251
And Master Ye's enemy
came to the door too.

26:45.570 --> 26:50.211
To avoid disrupting the banquet,
I brought both him and Master Ye back.

26:52.770 --> 26:53.810
Prince Li was also there

26:55.211 --> 26:56.251
at the birthday banquet.

26:59.330 --> 27:00.130
Your Highness.

27:01.610 --> 27:02.691
We have a lead.

27:03.810 --> 27:05.691
Yuan Fang died on the capital outskirts.

27:05.850 --> 27:09.011
After the crime, the killer
had only two options.

27:09.971 --> 27:12.330
First, flee the capital immediately.

27:12.610 --> 27:15.770
Second, be bold enough
to go against expectations

27:15.971 --> 27:17.011
and hide in the capital.

27:18.011 --> 27:20.411
On the day Yuan Fang was killed,
His Majesty was furious

27:20.491 --> 27:22.330
and ordered all major roads
blocked right away.

27:22.651 --> 27:25.411
The 13 capital garrisons searched
the outskirts for half a month

27:25.530 --> 27:27.370
and couldn't even find
a trace of the killer.

27:27.971 --> 27:30.411
So, I boldly speculate

27:31.850 --> 27:35.171
the killer went against expectations
and hid inside the city.

27:35.290 --> 27:37.971
Among the entry records
of those two days,

27:41.011 --> 27:46.251
a group claiming to be herb merchants
from Cangbei was highly suspicious.

27:46.891 --> 27:49.171
They entered the city
at the dawn after the crime.

27:49.691 --> 27:53.171
The first to be sealed off would surely
be the East Gate, closer to Wan'an.

27:55.411 --> 27:57.411
They seemed to go the long way around

27:57.891 --> 27:59.451
but were avoiding the main risk.

27:59.570 --> 28:01.050
Gao Wenhuan's personal guard said

28:01.130 --> 28:02.850
that in the chaos, he glimpsed

28:03.011 --> 28:06.211
that one of the killers had
extremely rare jade-green eyes.

28:07.171 --> 28:08.610
Our men kept watch day and night.

28:09.011 --> 28:12.171
Today, we found this group
at a Hu wine shop in Penglai Alley.

28:12.171 --> 28:15.050
Coincidentally, among them
there is a man with jade-green eyes.

28:18.691 --> 28:21.691
Muster the Jingzhao Prefecture guards
at once and send orders to Wang Suwu.

28:21.971 --> 28:24.691
Tonight, we'll capture them all.

28:25.011 --> 28:25.810
Yes.

28:31.651 --> 28:32.931
Ye Ying has also returned.

28:33.491 --> 28:35.330
Why don't you go to her room?

28:37.491 --> 28:42.011
You want to hear me say
that between you two, I like you more

28:42.011 --> 28:44.050
and just want to be with you, right?

28:44.691 --> 28:45.931
That's not true.

28:46.850 --> 28:49.731
I just like this room
and this courtyard.

28:50.691 --> 28:53.691
Even when you weren't back,
I liked coming here.

28:54.330 --> 28:55.651
East of the mansion,

28:57.330 --> 29:00.530
or maybe south, there's a pampas grove.

29:00.691 --> 29:02.171
This is the closest spot.

29:02.451 --> 29:05.691
Every year around this time,
after the pampas bloom,

29:05.891 --> 29:09.731
the fluff blown into the courtyard
is just like snow.

29:10.050 --> 29:11.130
It's so beautiful.

29:14.050 --> 29:14.850
Your Highness.

29:15.251 --> 29:16.050
Let's go.

29:23.610 --> 29:24.570
What's this?

29:25.330 --> 29:27.330
Poison. Drink it and you die.

29:27.491 --> 29:29.931
This is a calming soup.
Drink it and you sleep better.

29:30.491 --> 29:32.530
It's sweet? Sweet soup?

29:42.171 --> 29:43.050
The wind is up.

29:47.211 --> 29:48.971
It's snowing! It's snowing!

29:48.971 --> 29:49.610
Really.

29:50.011 --> 29:50.971
- Qingyu!
- It's snowing.

29:50.971 --> 29:52.731
Look!

29:53.011 --> 29:53.731
Wonderful.

29:54.130 --> 29:55.491
- It's snowing!
- Doesn't it look like snow?

29:57.530 --> 29:58.530
It's snowing.

30:19.931 --> 30:21.931
Your Highness, it's confirmed.

30:22.130 --> 30:24.330
That killer with jade-green eyes
is called Red Fox.

30:24.891 --> 30:27.770
He and his accomplices are holed up
in the residential house ahead.

30:28.931 --> 30:30.891
Military Secretary Wang
has this area surrounded.

30:30.891 --> 30:32.251
We're waiting for your order.

31:21.171 --> 31:21.731
Who's there?

31:33.050 --> 31:35.090
What's wrong?
Why have you come late at night?

31:35.411 --> 31:36.491
Red Fox has been exposed.

31:36.491 --> 31:37.211
What?

31:37.850 --> 31:40.731
The Yuan Fang case may surface.
His Highness should be prepared.

31:57.290 --> 32:00.370
Your Highness, you're awake.
Does your head hurt?

32:03.491 --> 32:05.330
Why are you looking at me like that?

32:10.251 --> 32:13.290
It's nothing. I had a dream.

32:18.411 --> 32:19.330
It's late.

32:19.770 --> 32:22.330
Since you're awake,
why not come to my room?

32:25.090 --> 32:28.330
They are something else.
How could they help you here?

32:34.491 --> 32:35.330
Your Highness.

32:38.411 --> 32:39.090
Your Highnesses.

32:44.891 --> 32:47.370
Ye Ying, go back to your room first.

32:59.850 --> 33:01.931
Your Highness, Red Fox has been exposed.

33:42.050 --> 33:43.451
Do as I say obediently.

33:43.610 --> 33:45.491
Or your dirty secrets will be exposed.

34:00.651 --> 34:01.451
Come in.

34:04.330 --> 34:06.251
Princess, Master Wenhua
requests your presence.

34:08.090 --> 34:10.411
My lady, should I
still go to Yanru Pond?

34:10.411 --> 34:12.170
Stay here. You don't need to go.

34:12.411 --> 34:13.210
Yes.

34:22.690 --> 34:24.491
Ye Ying sent you to find me, didn't she?

34:27.291 --> 34:29.891
Go tell her to meet me at Yanru Pond.

34:30.090 --> 34:30.931
Yes.

34:38.931 --> 34:39.730
Ye Li.

34:42.291 --> 34:44.090
Speak. What is it this time?

34:45.090 --> 34:46.530
You're asking me what's wrong?

34:47.570 --> 34:48.811
You've gone too far.

34:51.931 --> 34:54.851
Ye Li, you studied at Lishan Academy.

34:55.331 --> 34:56.971
Didn't they teach you any decency?

34:57.840 --> 35:00.016
My husband broke off the engagement
with you long ago.

35:00.090 --> 35:01.891
But you, still bitter, keep pestering

35:01.891 --> 35:04.130
and seducing my husband.
What exactly are you up to?

35:05.291 --> 35:06.851
Did you order the assassination?

35:11.011 --> 35:14.130
Do you know the penalty
by law for a hired assassination

35:14.491 --> 35:15.570
against a princess consort?

35:19.331 --> 35:20.931
Chu Code with Commentary states,

35:21.210 --> 35:22.570
"Among all accomplices,

35:22.730 --> 35:24.112
the mastermind is the principal.

35:24.331 --> 35:26.050
This crime is among
the Ten Abominations,

35:26.050 --> 35:27.451
unforgivable even by amnesty."

35:28.170 --> 35:31.250
Don't try to scare me.
I didn't do anything.

35:31.690 --> 35:32.851
I don't even know him.

35:33.331 --> 35:35.730
You brought it on yourself,
yet you blame me?

35:37.250 --> 35:40.331
I only said 'assassination.'
I didn't say how many killers.

35:40.690 --> 35:41.771
How do you know it was one?

35:46.050 --> 35:47.891
Mo Jingli and I are long over.

35:48.331 --> 35:49.491
I have no feelings for him.

35:49.931 --> 35:52.130
If you truly care this much
about this marriage,

35:52.491 --> 35:53.931
then you should restrain him

35:53.931 --> 35:55.851
instead of ranting at me
again and again.

35:57.170 --> 35:59.690
Ye Ying, my patience has limits.

36:00.291 --> 36:01.451
You'd better watch yourself.

36:04.011 --> 36:06.210
Ye Li, don't get too cocky.

36:06.960 --> 36:09.011
You Lishan people think
you're so high and mighty.

36:09.011 --> 36:10.451
You are just fame-seekers.

36:10.570 --> 36:12.451
Neither you nor your mother
are any good.

36:13.730 --> 36:15.050
For a woman like you,

36:15.210 --> 36:18.570
if Prince Ding knows what you've done,
he'll make you pay dearly.

36:20.371 --> 36:21.331
How dare you hit me!

36:21.730 --> 36:24.090
Why wouldn't I?
You're the one I'm teaching a lesson.

36:28.011 --> 36:29.130
I haven't hit you yet.

36:31.130 --> 36:31.931
Don't cry.

36:32.690 --> 36:34.451
So that's why you brought an umbrella.

36:35.090 --> 36:36.210
You meant to hit me.

36:39.090 --> 36:40.050
Not really.

36:41.331 --> 36:42.291
It'll rain tonight.

36:47.690 --> 36:48.530
What are you doing?

36:50.491 --> 36:52.371
Sometimes I really can't figure you out.

36:53.570 --> 36:54.971
What exactly do you like about him?

36:55.491 --> 36:56.690
His guqin playing skills?

36:57.250 --> 36:58.451
His so-called talent?

36:58.891 --> 37:00.690
Or that flashy,
good-for-nothing face of his?

37:02.210 --> 37:05.090
Your wedding day was the first time
you ever saw him, wasn't it?

37:06.291 --> 37:08.530
You know nothing about the man
who shares your bed.

37:09.491 --> 37:11.170
You don't know what he's thinking

37:11.491 --> 37:13.050
and what he's going to do.

37:13.451 --> 37:16.811
And you have no idea
beneath that gentle, refined exterior

37:16.811 --> 37:18.210
what kind of heart he really has.

37:19.050 --> 37:20.690
Do you actually love him,

37:21.491 --> 37:24.130
or just the illusion you've created
in your own mind?

37:25.730 --> 37:26.931
Of course I know.

37:27.570 --> 37:30.650
My husband has the whole world
in his heart. You can't slander him.

37:32.090 --> 37:33.971
Is that what he should have in heart?

37:34.570 --> 37:36.250
The world belongs to His Majesty.

37:38.771 --> 37:41.650
We are sisters.
That's why I'm telling you all this.

37:42.451 --> 37:43.931
But you simply refuse to believe it.

37:45.090 --> 37:48.331
Mo Jingli is far from
what you imagine him to be.

37:51.210 --> 37:52.730
Don't speak of him like that!

38:19.170 --> 38:19.971
Your Highness,

38:21.331 --> 38:22.451
everything is ready.

38:22.491 --> 38:24.050
All four alley entrances are sealed.

38:26.250 --> 38:27.050
Close in.

38:27.730 --> 38:28.491
Yes.

41:29.771 --> 41:30.451
Go!

41:34.800 --> 41:35.504
After them!

41:45.931 --> 41:46.730
How is it?

41:47.130 --> 41:48.050
I'm fine.

41:48.331 --> 41:49.331
Get him treated.

41:49.331 --> 41:49.831
- Yes.
- Yes.

41:54.130 --> 41:56.451
Your Highness, they're heading west.

42:00.411 --> 42:01.250
Pass my order:

42:01.811 --> 42:05.690
Close the gates of Chongren, Shengye,
and Yongxing wards immediately.

42:05.931 --> 42:07.050
Lock down the entire city.

42:07.730 --> 42:09.971
Take my token
and search along the canals.

42:10.331 --> 42:13.050
I want them alive or dead.

42:13.090 --> 42:13.931
Yes.

42:37.931 --> 42:38.811
Put it aside.

42:40.432 --> 42:44.112
(Preview)

42:44.570 --> 42:46.011
Wanzhou is really back.

42:46.371 --> 42:47.250
She's back.

42:48.570 --> 42:49.451
Wenhua,

42:50.210 --> 42:52.931
long time no see. How have you been?

42:54.851 --> 42:57.690
To whom did you give the edict summoning
Heiyun Cavalry to the capital?

42:57.690 --> 42:59.730
I... I...

43:00.210 --> 43:03.170
It's only right for me
to purge my own household.

43:03.530 --> 43:06.650
Now, it's time
to settle this sinful debt.

43:15.297 --> 43:21.889
♪Memories hold you back
from fulfilling your dreams♪

43:25.473 --> 43:31.617
♪Only by moving forward
can you find reunion♪

43:33.825 --> 43:37.057
♪Endings only mark new routes♪

43:37.281 --> 43:43.297
♪It's all part of the scenery♪

43:43.617 --> 43:47.041
♪To the horizon's call♪

43:47.105 --> 43:53.665
♪Your journey hasn't started♪

43:54.721 --> 43:58.657
♪Towards mountains,
chase the stars bright♪

43:58.657 --> 44:04.353
♪Both joy and grief
make the trip worthwhile♪

44:04.865 --> 44:13.473
♪Trying to catch up
to your own lost shadow♪

44:14.369 --> 44:19.873
♪Within the wilds, echoes thrive♪

44:19.873 --> 44:25.377
♪Clear mind leads to a clear path♪

44:25.441 --> 44:29.505
♪Be grateful to your losses♪

44:29.793 --> 44:35.017
♪Make your steps weightless♪

44:35.617 --> 44:39.329
♪Towards mountains,
chase the stars bright♪

44:39.361 --> 44:45.025
♪Let time embrace you
and wash away the past♪

44:45.793 --> 44:53.761
♪Put every twist behind you,
drift leisurely through time♪

44:55.169 --> 45:00.417
♪Make headway against the wind,
let mountains bow to your pace♪

45:00.673 --> 45:06.577
♪Rush towards a life without regret♪

45:06.577 --> 45:10.697
♪Let your nature burst free♪

45:10.913 --> 45:15.649
♪Unbound by form♪

45:16.865 --> 45:21.137
♪Let your nature burst free♪

45:21.377 --> 45:26.817
♪Unbound by form♪
